Today is Tuesday, the class is professor Yu’s. 

Before we started our class, I thanked our brother for his delicious food, for I just mentioned once, and he prepared a bag of that food for me. 

I took out my iPad today and contacted my mom, she said about her delay payment, that she shouldn’t care about money, if she pays attention to money, she can’t live her life. Thus she didn’t keep her eyes open to money, and concentrate on the life which God gave her. She believes in God, not God’s money. Such as, I believe in the promises of God and God’s image, but not the promised things. 

But the delay fulfillment of promises is common, to see our heart is adhering to money or God. We shouldn’t pay attention to money more than God, but pay attention to God and ignore the money, believe in God even without money. 

So, I can’t follow that pastor, because he has no word of eternal life, if he has, I can follow him without any money promise, but because he has no word of eternal life, although he promises money or gives me money on the spot, I can hardly follow him. 

The main features of Gospel, first is prophetic promises of Jesus Christ, second is the kingdom of God, Jesus Christ’s person and work, third is the cross and resurrection. 
prophetic预言性的；预示的 预言者的，先知的，预言的 
Deification through Christ, we received righteousness by his resurrection. Deification means the condition of being treated like a god. an embodiment of the qualities of a god. the capitalists' deification of capital. the elevation of a person as to the status of a god. 
Deification把…神化 embodiment（体现思想、品质或情感的）具体形象，化身 具体表现，体现 capitalist资本家 elevation提高，抬起；提升，晋升 
God raised Jesus from the dead, he is the true and only Messiah, the Father and the Spirit testify that he is the Messiah. 

The death of death in the death and resurrection of Christ. 

Three methods to get to know the attributes of God, first is the negative method, such as God is not human, God is not evil. Second is the Eminence method, such as God is our Father. Third is causality method, God created the world so God is creater, God saved us so God is our savior. 
Eminence著名，卓越，出众 causality因果关系
The communicable attributes means such attributes belong to God and also humans. The incommunicable attributes of God means those attributes just belong to God. But someone said all attributes are communicable and also incommunicable, like our brother had said. We are the image of God, but we are not God, we have those attributes inside to a certain extent. 

Some incommunicable attributes, such as Spirituality, Simplicity, Eternity, Immutability, Omnipresence, Omniscience. Immutability means The state or quality of being immutable; immutableness. The state of being unchangeable in the memory after creation. Omnipresence means The ability to be at all places at the same time; usually only attributed to God. Omniscience means the state of being omniscient; having infinite knowledge. 
Immutability不可改变 Omniscience无所不知的 Omnipresence广布的；普遍存在的 （上帝）无所不在的 
The delay fulfillment may be a better fulfillment, such as the thanks I don’t give my brother who brings food to me in messenger, but I thanked him late in class before all the students. 

I admired my leader with my sisters, he knows almost everything we are about to learn. Most importantly, he serves us like our servant, so he is our leader according to the word of our Lord Christ Jesus. 

Communicable attributes include knowledge, wisdom, good, spirituality, love, holy, righteousness, truthfulness, sovereignty. 

God’s name means his attributes, his essence and his being. You shall not take the name of Yahweh your God in vain, thus Jews even don’t dare to read the name of God in Holy Scripture, instead of the pronunciation of God’s name, they pronounced his name as Adonai. 

There is good, and absolute goodness means God, there is holy, and absolute holiness means God. There are many attributes of God, but these are one attribute, because our God is One. 

Almost all languages connected heaven with the conception of God. The name of God is plural, but he is one, so this form of plural is called majesty plural. 

The name of God is too holy to be pronounced, so they don’t pronounce this name and even don’t write down this name just leave a blank, or use the word LORD, all alphabet of this word is capitalization. This name has a term called Tetragrammaton. 
（希伯来人）表示上帝的四字母词（由四个辅音字母组成，即YHWH或JHVH，发音同Yahweh或Jehovah）
Tetragrammaton is the Hebrew name of God transliterated in four letters as YHWH or JHVH and articulated as Yahweh or Jehovah. 
（希伯来人）表示上帝的四字母词（由四个辅音字母组成，即YHWH或JHVH，发音同Yahweh或Jehovah）transliterate把（字母，单词）音译成另一语言体系中相应的字母（单词)，按另一字母体系印出 articulate流利连贯地表达(观点，感觉） 
God said that “I AM who I AM”, he decided his name, his name was expressed in his action, he is absolute one, he reveals himself in his name. His name is revelation of love, a covenant, a redemptive history. 

Our God is a king of majesty and glory. His majesty in his power, his absolute. His glory means his essence, his salvation, and his ethics. He expresses these by redemption. 
ethics行为准则；道德准则 
God’s name was expressed a lot in Isaiah 43:1-13. 

I asked my mom about her bank account, because she didn’t get any money after she came to South Korea, whether her salary or the reimbursement of travel and quarantine expenses. But I got 900,000 won this month. 
reimbursement偿还，向（花钱或损失金钱之人）偿付；给报销 偿还（所花或损失的钱）；报销（一笔钱） 
